      <title>美联储押注导致印尼债券收益率自 11 月以来跌幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/indonesian-bond-yields-drop-most-since-november-on-fed-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼债券收益率出现 11 月份以来最大跌幅，跑赢亚洲同行，原因是美国降息押注的复苏刺激了对上个月债券遭到大量抛售的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/indonesian-bond-yields-drop-most-since-november-on-fed-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 05:17:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
